text: Cailee Spaeny (; born July 24, 1998) is an American actress. She is known for her role as Priscilla Presley in the biographical movie Priscilla (2023). She was nominated for a Golden Globe Award for this role. She also appeared in Pacific Rim Uprising (2018), Bad Times at the El Royale (2018), On the Basis of Sex (2018), Vice (2018), The Craft: Legacy (2020), Devs (2020), Mare of Easttown (2021), Civil War (2024) and Alien: Romulus (2024). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Knoxville, Tennessee
